{"tid":1509960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關心警察子女 由家暴開始","createTime":"2019-08-27T04:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T05:18:51.000Z","uid":312942,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc50699e6e5a355019c8d600ec50d6d20bb1bab","tid":1509960,"uid":312942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:12:49.000Z","msg":"細時隔離屋的老豆是當差的，見佢成日都畀佢老豆打罵和趕出街，根本好多當差的教細路都淨係識用拳頭，所以應該有唔少家暴個案。而近來佢地要頻密OT，又keep住畀人罵黑警，肯定會更加暴燥，更容易發洩落仔女到。<br />\n<br />\n無端被打罵肯定想討回公道的，所以大家應該要做好文宣，鼓勵被父母打的警察子女挺身舉報。記住要令警察子女覺得你關心佢，佢地先會透露內情，先有機會教到佢地點樣記錄被打的日期、時間、地點、場合和受傷的情況，以及拍照留記錄。<br />\n<br />\n應該無野心傷得過畀自己仔女「出賣」~"},{"pid":"687fc03c0aded7f6d3d93ffd32712c47569415e0","tid":1509960,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左今天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6e105f1d773590111e1549ac1d81bd1c904b6f92","tid":1509960,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"快過呂麗乳搖"},{"pid":"b9cb2e4753ae165a69ac86eb1e34c3ae8d8368a7","tid":1509960,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=60b44555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou